OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing through the evening, these
OL,7,Foften heavy, but becoming lighter and
OL,8,Fgradually easing through the second
OL,9,Fpart of the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first on
OL,12,FWednesday, but some brighter spells
OL,13,Fdeveloping at times. A few spots of
OL,14,Frain possible where the cloud thickens.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FCloudy to start Thursday but gradually
OL,18,Fturning brighter later. Very warm on
OL,19,FFriday and Saturday, with more in the
OL,20,Fway of sunshine, although some
OL,21,Fthundery showers are possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
